  "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "Derived from WebArena Verified, SWE-Gym/SWE-bench-slice evidence, MiniWoB++ workloads, and released artifact processing outputs.",
  "prov:wasGeneratedBy": "Generated by evidence gating, redaction, validation, checksum generation, Croissant metadata construction, and claim-map construction workflows.",
  "rai:dataBiases": "Workload and task-family selection reflects WebArena Verified, SWE-Gym/SWE-bench-derived slices, and MiniWoB++ coverage only.",
