  "rai:dataSocialImpact": "Improves reproducibility and evidence discipline; misuse risk exists if interpreted as a model-capability leaderboard, mitigated by explicit claim boundaries.",
  "rai:dataUseCases": "Artifact review, reproducibility inspection, benchmark substrate inspection, and downstream agent-systems studies.",
  "rai:hasSyntheticData": "Some fixture or smoke materials may exist for validation, but they are not paper-facing and are excluded from quantitative aggregates.",
  "rai:personalSensitiveInformation": "No intentional personal data is included. Credential files, cookie jars, request header values, browser state exports, and raw sessions are excluded; samples are redacted.",
